attributes.action: Urge the UN to send a UN Peacekeeping Force to Ukraine immediately.
attributes.additional_details: Millions have been made refugees, and many have died. The UK Government has a responsibility to take whatever action it can to protect the people of Ukraine.
attributes.background: UK lobby and propose to the United Nations that an all Nations Peacekeeping force is immediately sent to Ukraine to protect the people of Ukraine.
